==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Omnium-gatherum
<hw>Om`ni*um-gath"er*um</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[A
macaronic compound of L. <ets>omnium</ets>, gen. pl. of <ets>omnis</ets>
all, and E. <ets>gather</ets>.]</ety> <def>A miscellaneous collection of
things or persons; a confused mixture; a medley; a hodgepodge.</def>
<mark>[Colloq. & Humorous]</mark> <rj><au>Selden.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> hotchpotch, odds and ends, farrago, motley
collection.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Omnivagant</ent>⟦br⟧
